  "title": "Childcare Supervisor at Serangoon/Ang Mo Kio",
  "description": "<p><strong>SALARY will depend on :</strong></p><p>1) no. of years of experience in this childcare industry</p><p><u><strong>POSITION:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Supervisor Role or Assistant Supervisor Role depending on the years of experience</li><li>Located in Serangoon and Ang Mo Kio  (walking distance to Mrt)</li></ul><p><u><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Located at Serangoon(next to mrt station)</strong></u></p><ul><li>Mentor a team of teachers, highlight their strengths and provide regular feedbacks for professional development.</li><li>Collaborate and work closely with parents and teachers to address children's learning needs.</li><li>Respond to parents' enquiries and feedbacks</li><li>Well acquaint with ECDA CMS through children enrollement and subsidy applications</li><li>Aligned Centre's standards and quality with SPARKS requirement</li><li>To lead a team and report to the centre director/manager</li><li>To be independent and to work closely with the management</li><li>To be active in enrollment of children</li><li>Conduct frequent meetings with teachers</li><li><br /></li></ul><p><u><strong>BENEFITS</strong></u></p><p>Annual Leave, Performance Bonus, Monthly Incentives Payout</p><p><u><strong>QUALIFICATIONS:</strong></u></p><p>Leadership Certificate in early childhood</p><p><br /></p><p>Salary will depends on number of years of experience</p><p><br /></p><p>Email resume to : cecilia@learningkidz.com.sg and state the salary</p><p>Contact me at : 90690910 (cecilia)</p>",
